{"tid":311006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華斥印度軍首度越境促撤離","createTime":"2017-07-06T08:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T00:05:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc530448650312d6f4307cecba1252a8d842377","tid":311006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170706/20080511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170706%2F20080511&d=3NzjFrGZfXEbbcbOPorIbKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=8cc5ce19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170706%2F20080511&h=6dbfbd36\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170706/20080511</a><br />\n<br />\n華斥印度軍首度越境促撤離<br />\n<br />\n5,785<br />\n <br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【中印對峙】<br />\n中印邊境（圖）對峙持續！中國駐印度大使羅照輝接受印媒採訪時表示，這是印軍首次越過已定邊界，入侵中國領土，形成兩軍近距離對峙，至前日已過去19天，洞朗地區形勢仍未得到緩解。這是錫金段邊界第一次出現如此嚴重事態。<br />\n羅照輝認為，今次事件是否引發戰爭，取決於印度政府的政策。中國外交部發言人表示，印軍應立即撤回邊界線一側，以避免事態更加嚴重。<br />\n羅照輝重申中方立場，指根據1890年《中英會議藏印條約》規定，洞朗地區毫無疑問屬於中國領土。該條約是中國承認錫金現狀的基礎。印度獨立後繼承了這一歷史界約。這次是印軍首次越界，也與過去雙方部隊在未定界線地區發生磨擦有本質上的區別。<br />\n他也駁斥印度有關「洞朗屬於不丹」的說法，強調洞朗屬於中國，「一直在中國有效管轄之下」，中不雙方對此不存在分歧。<br />\n對於印度外交部指摘中方在洞朗地區修築道路屬「改變現狀」，羅說，中方在洞朗地區活動是「中國主權範圍內的事，何來改變現狀？」印軍「越界闖入中國境內，改變了現狀」，只要印方撤出，現狀就能恢復。<br />\n<br />\n印美日軍演制華<br />\n此外，正當中印部隊在邊境對峙及中共海軍艦艇頻繁出沒印度洋之際，印度與日、美本月10日起將在孟加拉灣舉行馬拉巴爾聯合軍演。印度專家認為，此舉有遏阻中國海軍在印度洋意圖的效果。<br />\n中新社/中央社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n百度揸弗人涉違法乘無人車　辯稱有司機<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n台電視台老闆與女議員開房"},{"pid":"f8c2463ddbb255b2504f8757057a38856c3e6b8a","tid":311006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170706/large/06cf09p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F06cf09p.jpg&h=c8e87a11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b58a1171e71b8ed75fbc1e9db4b3ebe5fe06ef1b","tid":311006,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e47141555e7720b5d83fba416fb54054847f5d9","tid":311006,"uid":27363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東風21隨時侯命</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef785010862797dd4b2c20d29da82614882bcc47","tid":311006,"uid":22450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"《中英會議藏印條約》為歷史文件，已不具效力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1106457ea3a21bce4a517d02c3d5ed6fbbfc4d","tid":311006,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東風21隨時侯命</blockquote><br />\n烈火6隨時候命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722d3260691d99fa2c389882d023e0f4a037756a","tid":311006,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:17:08.000Z","msg":"雖遠必豬"},{"pid":"850d3879dfe830394e16c9a88cb646e9f94ad426","tid":311006,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"口交部好忙下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c94ab04ba37aa4234c9304be98ce3e97fbf1cc","tid":311006,"uid":5993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T23:51:07.000Z","msg":"點姐 你玩晒喇 一邊就唔承認歴史文件 一邊就叫人跟歷史文件去做"},{"pid":"f52f52ec737fdd64b44bf5a1c21fd71c22ac24b2","tid":311006,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T23:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖遠必豬</blockquote>